# Windows script/registry files must keep CRLF line endings VERBATIM:
# cmd.exe's goto/label scanning misbehaves in LF-only batch files and
# regedit expects CRLF in .reg imports. -text disables ALL git eol
# conversion so the committed CRLF bytes reach every checkout (and zip
# download) exactly as-is, regardless of anyone's core.autocrlf.
*.bat -text
*.reg -text
